  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0bae\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd; \u2019\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc7\u0bae\u0bcd\u2019",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Protest before Parliament; 'Ranilim Game'",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Ratindu Senaratne alias Ratta, one of the empty face protestors, has requested not to participate in the protest in front of the Parliament.",
        "We have been patiently fighting for more than 90 days. That patience should continue for another day or two.",
        "We have captured the President's House, the President's Secretariat and the Alary House. There is no need for us to touch on anything beyond this. Therefore, those who are protesting in front of the Parliament should return to empty-handed without causing further damage to public property.",
        "Those who struggle before Parliament should not fall into Ranil's game. He also said that this is Ranil's game."
      ],
